Package org.gvsig.gui.beans.panelGroup

Interface Summary
IPanelGroup All kind of panels which support a group of IPanel must implement this interface.
 

Class Summary
AbstractPanelGroup Represents a JPanel adapted to work with as a group of IPanel's.
PanelGroupManager Implemented to use the AbstractPanelGroup type desired.
Test1ExceptionsUsingTabbedPanel Tests the loading of layers using a TabbedPanel object and a PanelGroupLoaderFromList loader Tests also the managing of the different kind of exceptions which could be launched during this process.
Test1ExceptionsUsingTreePanel Tests the loading of layers using a TreePanel object and a PanelGroupLoaderFromList loader Tests also the managing of the different kind of exceptions which could be launched during this process.
Test1TabbedPanel Tests the creation of a TabbedPanel object using PanelGroupLoaderFromList .
Test1TreePanel Tests the creation of a TreePanel object using PanelGroupLoaderFromList .
TestPanelGroupLoaderFromList Tests PanelGroupLoaderUtilities and PanelGroupLoaderFromList.
TestPanelGroupManager Tests the class PanelGroupManager.
